{
  "id": "day-02",
  "day": 2,
  "kicker": "THE COPY · 02",
  "title": "The Upload Isn't You",
  "fps": 30,
  "width": 1080,
  "height": 1920,
  "durationInFrames": 1311,
  "palette": "signal",
  "voice": "en-US-EricNeural",
  "cta": "Follow if your own mind unsettles you.",
  "captions": [
    {
      "text": "They say one day you'll upload your mind and live forever.",
      "startMs": 100,
      "endMs": 4666
    },
    {
      "text": "But picture the machine that scans your brain, copies every neuron,",
      "startMs": 4616,
      "endMs": 9817
    },
    {
      "text": "and switches on.",
      "startMs": 9817,
      "endMs": 11235
    },
    {
      "text": "That copy wakes up certain it is you.",
      "startMs": 11235,
      "endMs": 14673
    },
    {
      "text": "It has your memories, your voice, your fear of dying.",
      "startMs": 14673,
      "endMs": 19474
    },
    {
      "text": "And meanwhile, you are still standing there.",
      "startMs": 19474,
      "endMs": 23210
    },
    {
      "text": "Or you died in the scan.",
      "startMs": 23210,
      "endMs": 25767
    },
    {
      "text": "Nothing transferred.",
      "startMs": 25767,
      "endMs": 28096
    },
    {
      "text": "You didn't become immortal.",
      "startMs": 28096,
      "endMs": 30639
    },
    {
      "text": "You built a stranger who inherits your life and your name.",
      "startMs": 30639,
      "endMs": 34957
    },
    {
      "text": "The upload isn't you.",
      "startMs": 34957,
      "endMs": 37329
    },
    {
      "text": "It's a successor who only thinks it is.",
      "startMs": 37329,
      "endMs": 40823
    }
  ],
